&lt;p&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to appoint to the post of Pathway Coordinator and Rota Coordinator within the Cardiology Department in the Integrated Medicine Division.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is an exciting opportunity for an enthusiastic and self-motivated individual to join the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will be responsible for providing secretarial/administrative support to the clinical team. You will also be working with the Cardiology consultants and registrar and rota’s to ensure a smooth running service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role will focus on supporting a positive patient experience within the service with a key emphasis on patient pathway tracking to achieve RTT standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work closely with the service team and receive support and training as required to fulfil the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameAhmad Arab HalabiJob titleService Delivery ManagerEmail addressahmad.arabhalabi@nhs.netTelephone number02088693736&lt;/p&gt;
